# MOGO Trading OS is a static, single-file application with no build step and no
# package manager -- this .gitignore is intentionally short and specific to what
# can actually appear in this project, not a generic bloated template.

# macOS
.DS_Store
.AppleDouble
.LSOverride
._*

# Windows
Thumbs.db
desktop.ini

# Editor/IDE swap and backup files
*.swp
*.swo
*~
*.bak
*.tmp

# Python (regression-baseline-tools.py is run locally, never packaged)
__pycache__/
*.pyc
*.pyo

# Local environment / secrets -- MOGO never stores API keys server-side (they live
# only in the browser's own localStorage, per docs/STORAGE_KEYS.md), but this is
# excluded defensively in case any local tooling ever introduces one.
.env
.env.local

# Claude Code / agent scratch and session artifacts -- these must never be committed.
# .claude/settings.local.json is a personal, machine-local permission allowlist (it
# accumulates references to this machine's own temp paths); .claude/launch.json is
# kept and tracked -- it's real, portable dev-server config. The project's actual
# test suites live under tests/ (see docs/TESTING.md); anything matching the
# patterns below is ephemeral working state from an AI coding session, never
# project content.
.claude/settings.local.json
*.scratchpad/
scratchpad/
